Megan Fox, 36, put on a busty display as she arrived at Vanity Fair's Oscars after-party in a plunging black velvet gown. The Hollywood star highlighted her ample assets in the figure-hutting number, with the gown featuring scalloped edging around her cleavage. Megan wore her dyed red tresses in loose waves and opted for a more natural makeup look with a glossy pink lip. She accessorised with a silver statement jewelled necklace, as before posing alongside Billie Eilish and other attendees. Megan made an appearance without her beau Machine Gun Kelly, amid rumours of trouble in their relationship, with the couple reportedly having daily Zoom therapy sessions.